# Queues & jobs

- Default queue connection is `database` (`config/queue.php`, `src/.env.example`).
- Redis exists locally (Sail `redis` service) but queue driver may still be database.

## Expectations when adding async work

- Be explicit about retries/timeouts and idempotency where it matters.
- Remember that tests run with `QUEUE_CONNECTION=sync` (`src/phpunit.xml`), so side effects happen inline during tests.
